<div class="pt-32 pb-20">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-6">
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl italic text-gray-900 mb-4">Returns & Exchange</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Our goal is to ensure you are completely satisfied with your purchase. Please read our return conditions below.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-8">
        
        <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 p-8 rounded-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="material-icons-outlined text-red-700 text-2xl mt-1">priority_high</span>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-red-800 mb-3">Check Before You Receive</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-bold">
                        You MUST check the product in front of the delivery man.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mt-2">
                        If you find any damage, defect, or mismatch, return it immediately to the delivery man. Once the delivery man leaves, we cannot accept any claims regarding damage or missing items.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="material-icons-outlined text-gray-800 text-2xl mt-1">autorenew</span>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900 mb-3">Replacements & Exchanges</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        If a damage is found during the check:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-3 pl-2">
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-gray-900">Same Item Replacement:</strong> If available in stock, we will replace the damaged item with a fresh one. 
                            <span class="inline-block bg-green-50 text-green-700 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded ml-2 uppercase">Free Delivery</span>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong class="text-gray-900">Exchange Options:</strong> If the item is out of stock, you may exchange it for a similar item of similar or higher price.
                        </li>
                        <li class="bg-gray-50 p-3 border border-gray-100 rounded text-xs text-gray-500">
                            <strong class="text-gray-800">Coupon Policy on Exchange:</strong> 
                            Coupons applied to the original (damaged) product will <u>not</u> be transferred to the new exchanged item if it is a different product. The new item will only be discounted if it has its own valid active coupon.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm">
                <span class="material-icons-outlined text-gray-800 text-2xl mb-4">local_shipping</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900 mb-3">Delivery Charges</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    In case of a return (where you do not take a replacement), the <strong>delivery charge is strictly non-refundable</strong>. You will be refunded the product cost only.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 p-8 rounded-sm shadow-sm">
                <span class="material-icons-outlined text-gray-800 text-2xl mb-4">schedule</span>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900 mb-3">Refund Timeline</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    If no replacement is possible and a refund is required, it will be processed within <strong>7-14 working days</strong> to your original payment method.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-gray-900 p-8 rounded-r-sm">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-900 mb-3">Payment Gateway Disclaimer</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">
                Niche Boutique is not responsible for any payment failures caused by technical glitches or server issues from the payment provider (e.g., bKash, Bank Servers).
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                If your money is deducted but the order is not confirmed due to a gateway error, please contact the respective Bank or Mobile Financial Service (bKash) authority directly.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>